 Duty的研究報告, 建議<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">英國政府應將BNO權利擴大至與BC同等</span></ins></strong>, 因為若BNO人成為BC, 這&rdquo;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>將會促使中國和平地行事</ins></strong></span>&rdquo; (p. 6), 香港人可以&rdquo;在自由的環境下生活, 而中國則失去一整代人,<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"> 英國會得到道德和物質上的勝利</span></ins></strong>&rdquo; (p. 7). 不只如此, <strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人&rdquo;人均收入高, 高學歷及具備專業技能, 對英國經濟會有實質益處</span></ins></strong>&rdquo; (p. 8). 最後, <strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">英國幫BNO升級可顯示英國&rdquo;並未忘記其角色和放棄原則&rdquo;</span></ins></strong> (p. 9). 這份報告暗示: a. BNO是&rdquo;和平時代&rdquo;的產物. 只要中英間利益衝突, BNO會是英國的招數: 中國領土內突然出現大批BC會<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">使英國有理由介入香港事務</span></ins></strong>, 這也是為什麼當初英國不給港人BC身份, 卻要弄出BNO, 而中國則要強加中國籍給香港人的根本原因 (英國不要收留港人; 中國收港人, 但條件是&rdquo;管得了&rdquo;的港人. 反正要抓人只要說句他是&rdquo;中國人&rdquo;就行) (結論1和3); b. 英國對香港的&rdquo;道義和責任&rdquo;乃建基在利益上, 尤其<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">正值英國脫歐, 香港將可成為英國經濟的救火員</span></ins></strong> (結論2)."},{"pid":"6d78be57a42790f049cf87c39147ebf7f69b6850","tid":1495992,"uid":119933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93ea632549955ec2e355b4e9b731bea639f3d9c7","tid":1495992,"uid":119933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:58:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/visa-waiver-program-vwp-should-be-given-british-national-overseas-passport-holder\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fvisa-waiver-program-vwp-should-be-given-british-national-overseas-passport-holder&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIacrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=498af087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/visa-waiver-program-vwp-should-be-given-british-national-overseas-passport-holder</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家支持和SHARE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:08:31.000Z","msg":"推，收到email啦"},{"pid":"7a08688d63d